Git Merge
================
git merge feature main

main branch commits are put into feature branch
safe :: existing branches are not changed

Git Rebase
================
git rebase feature main

feature branch commits are put into main - each commit in feature is a commit in main
cleaner project history

The golden rule of rebasing :: only use if no one else is working on the main branch


